						<div class="col-md-9">

							<H2>Truck Permits</h2>
								<A TARGET="NEW" HREF="https://drpa.aecomonline.net/"><IMG ALIGN="RIGHT" SRC="../images/travel_overweight-truck.png" ALT="Truck Permit" class="page_graphic"></a><h3>Overweight Vehicles</h3>



<p>All loads overweight (80,000 lbs. or more) require authorization. To apply for a truck permit, please click the link below. Once your application is submitted, the system will automatically approve or deny and notify DRPA Police and Toll. You will receive a confirmation email and it is recommended that the driver has this confirmation email in hand.</p>

<i class="fa fa-external-link"></i>&nbsp;<A TARGET="NEW" HREF="https://drpa.aecomonline.net/"><B>Truck Permit Application</B></A><br><i>*Required only if the load is over 80,000 lbs.</i>

<hr>
<h3>OVERSIZED VEHICLES</h3>
<P>If you are oversized and 80,000lbs or less, you are required to have a police escort and no authorization or permit is required.</P>

<b>Police escort:</b>
<UL>
<LI>Commodore Barry Bridge (856) 241-4801
<LI>Walt Whitman Bridge (215) 218-3701
<LI>Ben Franklin Bridge (856) 968-3301
<LI>Betsy Ross Bridge (856) 317-5901
</UL>


<hr>
<h3>TOLL SCHEDULE</h3>
<p>Tolls are paid by vehicles traveling westbound from New Jersey to Pennsylvania. Acceptable forms of payment are cash and <a href="/travel/e-zpass.html">E-ZPass</a>.</p>

<hr>
<h3>QUESTIONS?</h3>
<p>Please call (856) 241-4850.</p>



